body.description: Centrum Silver Women's Multivitamin for Women 50 Plus brings you a tailored multivitamin/multimineral supplement that contains micronutrients to help support full body wellness (1). This women's vitamin with iron contains essential nutrients, including vitamin D and calcium to support strong bones and B Vitamins to help promote heart health (1, 2). This multivitamin for women over 50 also contains zinc and B Vitamins to help support normal brain function and Vitamins A, C, and E for eye health (1, 2). Key micronutrients in these multivitamins with zinc supplements help fill in nutritional gaps to promote overall wellness and vitality (1). These women's vitamins are verified Non-GMO (3) and gluten free. This women's multivitamin with iron features a smooth coating that makes it easy to swallow. Simply take one multivitamin daily to provide your body with essential vitamins and minerals. Centrum Silver is the number 1 Doctor recommended multivitamin brand now shown to support memory and cognition in older adults (1).* * IQVIA: Claim substantiation Validation Statement. July 2023. IQVIA, using the ProVoice Survey, recorded the product recommended most often within the Adult Multivitamins category by physicians and pharmacists in the United States. A statistically significant majority of the panel of physicians and pharmacists responded that Centrum is the product they endorse most.(1) These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.(2) Not a replacement for cholesterol-lowering drugs (1) (3) Read more about our Non-GMO standard on Centrum's official website.

reviews.reviewText: The tablets are easy to swallow despite their size. They are not any larger than a normal vitamin but, they have a coating on them that makes them go down easily. Pretty good price I thought too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Trusted, Complete Vitamin and Mineral Supplement
reviews.reviewText: Centrum Vitamin/Mineral tablets offer an exceptionally complete combination of the most essential vitamins and minerals, without exceeding recommended dosages. They are very easy on the system, causing no discomfort whatsoever. We especially appreciated the generous amount of Vitamin B-12. These are the only supplements which never trigger our migraines. Definitely effective, over a period of days there is an apparent increase in energy, as well as more beneficial sleep. Very reasonable cost. Highly recommended

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars The only vitamin thus far that I can actually feel working!
reviews.reviewText: I read someplace that people were flocking to buy Centrum Silver Women's Multivitamin for Women, so I decided to try it. I actually started feeling more upbeat and energetic soon thereafter. I am reserving final judgment, but I am halfway through the bottle and my energy is still in evidence. I expect I will buy another bottle when this one is finished. My hope is that I continue to feel terrific!!
